    "descriptionHtml": "<h2>Twentyeighth</h2>\n<p>It’s been a busy couple of weeks. I moved to New Delhi not too long ago and I’m still in the middle of rebuilding my life here. I haven’t heard a lot of exceptional music, unfortunately (given the lack of time at hand). But this will have to do, for now.</p>\n<p><strong>Monday Music Mix: 28</strong></p>\n<p>Album art featuring work by <a href=\"http://pavelripley.com/\">Pavel Ripley</a></p>\n<p>Tracklist:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Javelin - Soda Popinski</li>\n<li>Beat Culture - Useless</li>\n<li>Ben Folds Five - Do It Anyway</li>\n<li>Haim - Go Slow</li>\n<li>Charlotte Gainsbourg - Anna</li>\n<li>Charli xcx - I’ll Never Know</li>\n<li>Air - Seven Stars</li>\n<li>Elika - No One Gets Lost</li>\n<li>Tiny Victories - Lost Weekend</li>\n<li>Dirty Three - Rising Below</li>\n<li>Led Er Est - Kaiyo Maru</li>\n<li>Gitar - Hippie Dream</li>\n<li>Polica - Lay Your Cards Out</li>\n<li>Grizzly Bear - Sleeping Ute</li>\n<li>The Lost Lovers Brigade - Lonely Neighbour</li>\n<li>Emika - Drop The Other</li>\n<li>Daughter - Love</li>\n<li>Catcall - Paralysed</li>\n<li>Harry Rag - Tiny Painting</li>\n<li>Feist - Black Tongue</li>\n<li>Major Lazer - Get Free (feat. Amber of Dirty Projectors)</li>\n</ol>\n<p>* Tracks in blue indicate my favourites</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.mediafire.com/?c6ywfbeevyed9jh\">Download album</a> | <a href=\"https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/96311/MMM-28.zip\">Mirror</a></p>",
